  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You bare forth the Rune of Water, and from it materialize the healing drop of kindness. When you cast this spell, your target gains the benefit of either @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Et8RSCLx8w7uOLvo]{Sound Body}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.EfFMLVbmkBWmzoLF]{Clear Mind} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.BCuHKrDeJ4eq53M6]{Sure Footing}. If you succeed on your counteract check to cure an ailment, the target is healed for 5d6 hit points.</p><p>If you cast this spell with 3 actions instead, you target a 20 foot burst and can heal creatures within the area of their ailments. You choose one of the three spells to affect all of the targets. If you succeed on a counteract check to cure an ailment on a creature, they are instead healed for 3d6 hit points.</p><p></p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The healing increases by 2d6 for both 2-action and 3-action versions of the spell.</p>"
